nderstanding of soft X-ray transient outbursts, state transitions and\nvariability in X-ray binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Apr 2003 08:19:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2003 15:40:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
