em. These simulations, based on\nadvanced GTD methods, are used to evaluate the straylight rejection of the\nentire optical system, by applying a new approach for evaluating the sidelobes\nin a rigorous way, even at very low levels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Apr 2003 13:07:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
